00:18:46,780 --> 00:18:47,960
Let's go get something nice.

376
00:18:48,399 --> 00:18:48,819
Watch your step.

377
00:19:03,460 --> 00:19:04,399
My Lord, please pardon me.

378
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:07,879
