00:19:10,819 --> 00:19:11,540
Yes, My Lord.

382
00:19:17,520 --> 00:19:18,260
Brother Cui,

383
00:19:18,359 --> 00:19:19,980
Nanling is such a lively place.

384
00:19:20,819 --> 00:19:21,720
Nanling

385
