486
00:25:12,940 --> 00:25:14,200
If you hadn't plotted against me,

487
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:15,420
I wouldn't care about you.

488
00:25:17,399 --> 00:25:18,579
Porridge is here.

489
00:25:24,480 --> 00:25:25,200
My father said

490
00:25:25,379 --> 00:25:26,740
